OL,3,CMum whose son drowned warns of cold
OL,4,Cwater danger after more teens die
OL,6,FA bereaved mother who lost her son to
OL,7,Fdrowning almost 20 years ago is
OL,8,Fwarning teenagers about the dangers of
OL,9,Fswimming in cold water after more
OL,10,Fdeaths in open water are reported
OL,11,Facross the UK during the recent hot
OL,12,Fweather.
OL,14,FMaxine Johnson's son, Reuben, drowned
OL,15,Fin 2006 whilst enjoying a day at
OL,16,FPontsticill Reservoir in Merthyr
OL,17,FTydfil.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
