CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1779981070
OL,3,CMum whose son drowned warns of cold
OL,4,Cwater danger after more teens die
OL,6,FThe 15-year-old was camping with
OL,7,Ffriends to celebrate the end of their
OL,8,FGCSEs before some decided to swim
OL,9,Facross the reservoir.
OL,11,FMs Johnson said that Reuben died after
OL,12,Fexperiencing cold water shock. She
OL,13,Fsaid: "Your body reacts to the
OL,14,Fcoldness of the water, and on a hot
OL,15,Fday like today and like when Reuben
OL,16,Fdied, the cold water shocks your body
OL,17,Fand you panic and struggle.
OL,19,F"If you can't control your breathing
OL,20,Fand the panic takes over, then you can
OL,21,Fdrown."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
