PN,46303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1779981070
OL,3,CMum whose son drowned warns of cold
OL,4,Cwater danger after more teens die
OL,6,FMs Johnson's warning comes as a 72-
OL,7,Fyear-old women died after being pulled
OL,8,Ffrom the water on West Angle Bay beach
OL,9,Fin Pembrokeshire on Sunday (24 May).
OL,10,FShe is the latest open water death
OL,11,Fconfirmed over this bank holiday
OL,12,Facross the UK, with seven children
OL,13,Falso having lost their lives.
OL,15,FThe bereaved mother explained how the
OL,16,Fnews of the recent drownings have been
OL,17,Fdifficult to process.
OL,19,F"It's quite sickening to be honest,"
OL,20,Fshe explained.
OL,26,@{D@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
