OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1779981070
OL,3,CMum whose son drowned warns of cold
OL,4,Cwater danger after more teens die
OL,6,F"I've not had much sleep in the last
OL,7,Fweek thinking about the families.
OL,9,F"It brings everything back to the day
OL,10,FReuben died."
OL,12,FMaxine said that the impact of
OL,13,FReuben's death haunts not only just
OL,14,Fthe family, but also his friends who
OL,15,Fsaw him disappear in the reservoir.
OL,17,FShe said: "His friends who were with
OL,18,Fhim have been traumatised and have
OL,19,Fbeen living with a lot all these years.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1779981070
OL,3,CMum whose son drowned warns of cold
OL,4,Cwater danger after more teens die
OL,6,F"They realised life can be snatched
OL,7,Faway in a few moments. They didn't
OL,8,Frealise how serious it was until they
OL,9,Fsaw Reuben disappear in the water."
OL,11,FAs a campaigner for drowning
OL,12,Fprevention, Ms Johnson is now calling
OL,13,Ffor consistent education for teenagers
OL,14,Fon how to stay safe around cold water.
OL,16,FShe said it is vital that all children
OL,17,Funderstand the risks of entering
OL,18,Fenvironments like reservoirs.
OL,20,F"There needs to be constant education
OL,21,Fabout this," she added.
